  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Powerful weapons<br></li><li> Headshots<br></li><li> Old-school<br></li><li> Fast paced</li></ul></p><br><h1>Upcoming updates</h1><p>The game still in development.<br>In future updates we're planning to add next features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Additional campaign missions<br></li><li> New game+<br></li><li>Endless game mode<br></li><li> Controller support</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.poster.avif?t=1600251030\" width=540 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.webm?t=1600251030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.mp4?t=1600251030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Zombies must die</strong> is a pile of fun!<br><br>In a bunch of manually created locations, you need to shoot all kinds of zombies in order to collect the documents left in this infected lab. To do this there is a huge arsenal of firearms that are necessary to blow up the zombie's brain (pun), <strong>Zombies must die</strong> provides a fun retro shooting from start to finish.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.poster.avif?t=1600251030\" width=540 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.webm?t=1600251030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359850/extras/0fdcf9b16e3ef32e2525242c775c1e2f.mp4?t=1600251030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Zombies must die</strong> is a pile of fun!<br><br>In a bunch of manually created locations, you need to shoot all kinds of zombies in order to collect the documents left in this infected lab. To do this there is a huge arsenal of firearms that are necessary to blow up the zombie's brain (pun), <strong>Zombies must die</strong> provides a fun retro shooting from start to finish.",
